            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Veneris Victricis <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>m</abbr><ex>unicipio</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>F</abbr><ex>lavio</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>C</abbr><ex>isimbrensi</ex></expan> beneficio <lb n="3"/><expan><abbr>Imp</abbr><ex>eratoris</ex></expan> Caesaris <expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>usti</ex></expan> <lb n="4"/><del rend="erasure">Domit<supplied reason="lost">iani</supplied> <expan><abbr>co</abbr><ex>n</ex><abbr>s</abbr><ex>ulis</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>c</abbr><ex>ivitatem</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>R</abbr><ex>omanam</ex></expan> con</del><lb break="no" n="5"/>sicutus <note>sic</note> per hono<lb break="no" n="6"/>rem <expan><abbr>IIvir</abbr><ex>atus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Q</abbr><ex>uintus</ex></expan> Anni<lb break="no" n="7"/>us <expan><abbr>Quir</abbr><ex>ina</ex></expan> Niger <lb n="8"/><expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>e</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>ua</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>ecunia</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>ono</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>edit</ex></expan>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Auf der Oberseite 3 Dübellöcher mit Bleiresten von der Befestigung der Statue. Es sind noch Zeilenlinien für die Beschriftung erkennbar. Buchstaben neuzeitlich mit weißer Farbe nachgezogen. (B): Gonzáles, AE 1981: Z. 4/5: [[Domitiani]] [c(ivitatem) R(omanam) con]/sicutus.</p>
            </div>
